originalText.text: I had the pleasure of working with Halucinated Studios (Steve Lucin) and his team for an experiential visual art and music event, and they really took the experience to the next level. Friendly, professional, and willing to work with you both technically and creatively. Could not have asked for a better creative team to work with and I am looking forward working with them again in the near future.

originalText.text: Steve (the owner and main designer/strategist) is truly an incredible branding genius! He has helped me completely transform my business and I couldn’t be more grateful. He has a very experienced team that mirror his energy. He is truly passionate about what he does; why would you want anyone else?! Halucinated Studios will find the solutions to the branding questions you don’t even know you have yet!

originalText.text:
Energy in this studio is unmatched. Meeting Steve to do any kind of work in his studio is simply amazing. He really takes the time to listen to your problem and he just offers some amazing soLUCIoNes.
Not all superheros wear capes, but they should all have a Steve Lucin.
Can you imagine if Batman had Steve as his branding guy?
Batman only has 243k on Instagram right now. That's because Steve didn't do any flyers, animations, websites, or branding work. Batman should have more followers than Will Smith by far. And he doesn't.
Don't see the problem yet? Do a discovery session with Steve, and come back and comment on this....I'll wait...
